            "description": "The modern enterprise is many things: a matrix structure, globalized, driven by distributed and virtual teams, and often needs to be highly engaged with communities. Come and hear how mobility can help ideas develop and coalesce to drive competitive advantage. ",
            "title": "Strategic Mobility in the Enterprise: Empowering Communities and Collaboration",
